00:03:16.020 --> 00:03:21.980
But I'll speak up
loud and hopefully

00:03:21.980 --> 00:03:26.810
gravitate towards this
theme of urban renewal.

00:03:26.810 --> 00:03:29.100
When Sean asked for
a title, I should

00:03:29.100 --> 00:03:32.880
have just said poetry reading.

00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:35.810
Now I have to frame my
