- Well if I'm not
mistaken, I think

01:15:50.490 --> 01:15:54.350
there's a small reception
just outside the room.

01:15:54.350 --> 01:15:58.520
So if you want to speak
directly with Major Jackson,

01:15:58.520 --> 01:16:01.185
then that's where you can
do it for a little while,

01:16:01.185 --> 01:16:01.810
if he holds up.

01:16:01.810 --> 01:16:03.820
- Yeah, I'm doing good.

01:16:03.820 --> 01:16:05.120
- Thank you very, very much.

01:16:05.120 --> 01:16:05.620
- Thank you.

